## ğŸ§ª **Tests**

### **Quick Execution**
```bash
# Quick verification
python tests/run_tests.py --type unit

# Tests with coverage
python tests/run_tests.py --coverage

# Or use CLI (after pip install -e ".[dev]")
ezqt test --unit
ezqt test --coverage
```

